        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Hammoleketh—or, the queen, as the Vulg. renders it, may be conceived of here as a half-sister and consort of Gilead.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
